{"tid":1081642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「年經」大家上網買點數真係唔好貪小便宜","createTime":"2019-03-28T11:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T12:15:58.000Z","uid":214417,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4256f23a618645ccfc4b1ed84729832117e50f77","tid":1081642,"uid":214417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"呢條友係Carousell開ac賣itunes google，第一次我用正帳見佢賣咁平咪問佢可唔可以面交，佢又堅持要用支付寶交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我同佢講面交收800$ 1張 收2張，佢又話不如1000幾賣哂2張比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我一睇就知係呃人啦。就話唔要。<br />\n隔1日見到有其他人係佢賣既post上話佢「騙子黎！會叫你用支付寶交易！」之後個騙子即刻刪文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開另一個ac,佢話自己新開店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我再望一望佢圖片，咁似樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後我無野做 就諗住起佢底，唔想佢呃到人錢，結果失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢已經接受左個價，聽朝就比負評，話佢騙徒，搞到佢死左個ac先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢可以繼續開ac,但我相信佢都會用呢個方法呃人！<br />\n所以勸告各位 一定要面交！<br />\n以下係騙徒詐騙手法<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3xon6i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3xon6i.png&h=4517f804&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxRXsxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxRXsxZ.png&h=75d289af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sETfec1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsETfec1.png&h=82d4145e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRKYWrn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRKYWrn.png&h=99423197&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1TvQNx3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1TvQNx3.png&h=65c46053&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDQAYEL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3